Cook,<br><br>
I think the rifle you're looking for may be a modified SKS.  We had one in our attic in the DaNang Ops building that someone had traded for, but no one couldn't figure a way of sneaking it home.  The guys who had traded for it said it was an &quot;SKS Sniper Rifle.&quot; I think it is still there.  <br><br>
You might look at the following web sites:<br><br>
http://www.nationlink.com/sksman/sksfaq/main.html<br>
http://amesp02.tamu.edu/~grimaila/recreation/sks/manual.html<br><br>
Good luck.
